1366
01:20:20,939 --> 01:20:22,705
- I loved your mama, Jared.

1367
01:20:22,705 --> 01:20:23,583
You gotta believe that,

1368
01:20:23,583 --> 01:20:24,416
- You divorced her.

1369
01:20:24,416 --> 01:20:26,399
