1405
01:21:58,739 --> 01:22:02,239
But, see man, you didn't just divorce her.

1406
01:22:03,438 --> 01:22:04,771
You divorced me.

1407
01:22:06,595 --> 01:22:09,012
And I hate you for that, man.

1408
01:22:09,928 --> 01:22:10,845
I hate you.

1409
01:22:32,602 --> 01:22:33,435
- 1988.

